      "span_text": "To determine the intracellular location of H. pylori and L. acidophilus, we applied deconvolution microscopy and analyzed the uptake of the bacteria with the early endosome marker EEA1 (34) and the late endosome and lysosome marker LAMP-1 [CITATION_1] ."
